assert_raises_message(errors.CompileException,
    "Named block 'x' not allowed inside of def 'foo'", Template,
    """
                <%def name="foo()">
                <%block name="x">
                    block
                </%block>

                foob

                <%block name="x">
                    block
                </%block>
                </%def>
            """
    )
